programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan 13 orang gadis yang bakal memberikan inspirasi. Dalam episod ini gadis inspirasinya ialah Fatiha Shuib seorang aktivis sosial dan pejuang pesakit mental. Beliau yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur merupakan pemegang ijazah sarjana muda syariah dari Jordan. Beliau bertugas sebagai seorang usahawan sosial di syarikatnya sendiri. Beliau merupakan penghidap pesakit bipolar dan adhd. Veliau mula berminat dengan kerja-kerja sosial semasa belajar di Jordan.

programme.title: Galaksi Ep7
programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Setiap episod mengandungi 3 segmen iaitu Tajuk Utama, Tahukah Anda (membawa trivia dan fakta menarik) dan Eksperimen (yang boleh dilakukan di rumah). Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim membawa penonton meneroka fenomena Kerdipan Bintang, mengenali objek-objek langit yang memancarkan cahaya dan terdiri daripada nebula, serta memahami pengkelasan bintang. Dalam segmen Tahukah Anda, penonton akan mengetahui bahawa Malaysia telah diberi penghormatan untuk menamakan sebuah bintang. Segmen Eksperimen pula mengajar cara membina Rajah HR untuk memahami klasifikasi bintang dengan lebih jelas.

programme.desc: Aisyah dibesarkan dengan adat Melayu dan pantang larang. Ketika anak-anak dan suaminya mengamalkan cara hidup moden, timbul konflik keluarga. Akhirnya, Aisyah sedar bahawa kasih sayang lebih penting daripada mematuhi adat lama. Pak Ayob telah dimasukkan ke hospital akibat serangan jantung. Aisyah dan Wardina bersama-sama menjaganya di hospital. Zana berazam untuk mempertahankan rumahtangganya walaupun Firdaus tetap ingin memperisterikan Wardina. Kidah pula semakin rapat dengan Ucop, dan terus melaporkan keadaan Pawi kepada Ucop. programme.desc: Sebuah program majalah yang membawa penonton meneroka rahsia alam semesta dari aspek sains, teknologi dan sejarah. Setiap episod mengandungi 3 segmen iaitu Tajuk Utama, Tahukah Anda (membawa trivia dan fakta menarik) dan Eksperimen (yang boleh dilakukan di rumah). Episod kali ini Hos Amirul Hazim, membawa penonton mengkaji penggunaan Buruj sebagai Navigasi dalam proses menentukan arah dan kedudukan untuk mencari destinasi. programme.title: Persada Jurnal
programme.desc: Dokumentari ini membawa penonton meneroka peranan Jabatan Hal Ehwal Agama Islam Negeri Sembilan (JHEAINS) dalam usaha menyantuni masyarakat, khususnya komuniti Orang Asli dan golongan asnaf. Merentasi negeri yang kaya dengan warisan budaya ini, dokumentari ini memaparkan komitmen JHEAINS dalam membawa transformasi kepada masyarakat. Mesej perpaduan dan keberkesanan pendekatan santun yang dibawa oleh JHEAINS menjadi tema utama yang meresapi keseluruhan naratif. Dokumentari ini bukan sekadar merakam sebuah program, tetapi menjadi testimoni kepada pendekatan holistik JHEAINS dalam membangunkan ummah. Ia adalah bukti bahawa melalui pendekatan yang santun dan program yang terancang, perpaduan dapat dipupuk dan kehidupan masyarakat dapat ditransformasi. Saksikan Persada Jurnal dengan tajuk Kembara Perpaduan Madani.

programme.title: 1 Anugerah Ep8
programme.desc: Bersama hos Fiona Cheong menjelajah ke lokasi pilihan dalam negara. Episod ini membawa penonton ke Paya Indah Wetlands di Selangor Darul Ehsan yang merupakan kawasan seluas 450 hektar yang terkenal dengan keindahan alam semulajadinya. Bekas kawasan perlombongan ini mempunyai 14 buah tasik yang dikawalselia oleh Jabatan Perhilitan. Fiona Cheong berkongsi tentang tarikan yang terdapat di kawasan ini seperti pemuliharaan badak air, buaya tembaga, landak, itik belibis dan ratusan jenis ikan. Kawasan ini juga merupakan habitat kepada 245 spesis burung.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep03
programme.desc: Rian tidak yakin dengan Adif, terutamanya kerana Adif sering mengusiknya sebagai anak orang kaya yang mengada, sombong, penting diri sendiri. Rian terkejut apabila rombongan merisik Adif tiba tanpa sebarang perbincangan terlebih dahulu. Adif meminta maaf dan berjanji akan lebih terbuka. Namun, cemburu melihat Adif bersama Rian menyebabkan Afeeq menasihati Rian untuk membatalkan pertunangan. Semasa Rian Rian bercakap telefon dengan Adif, Afeeq menerjah menghalang Rian kahwin dengan Adif sebab dia cintakan Rian. Adif mendengar melalui talian telefon yang belum di off kan oleh Rian tanpa sengaja. Adif marah, menambah ketegangan dalam hubungannya dengan Rian dan sakit hati dengan Afeeq.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep04
programme.desc: Kisah bermula dengan pertengkaran Adif dan Afeeq kerana pengakuan Afeeq dan menghalang niat perkhawinan Adif kepada Rian. Rian leraikan dan yakinkan Adif, dia terima Adif saja. Majlis pertunangan berlangsung, tetapi Afeeq menunjukkan ketidakpuasan hati. Rian gembira ingin berkenalan dengan keluarga Adif tetapi Adif terus mengelak. Rina, sahabat Rian, meragui perkahwinannya dengan Fuad, namun Rian, Mun dan Nur Ain beri nasihat kepada Rina supaya jangan ovethinking. Adif, yang sebenarnya jatuh cinta dengan Rian, tertekan dan bimbang akan fokusnya lari, tetapi Sham menggalakkan Adif memanfaatkan peluang ini. Rian cuba berbaik dengan Afeeq dan meminta peluang, tetapi Afeeq menolak. Ketegangan meningkat apabila Adif abaikan Rian semula, menyebabkan Rian mahu membatalkan pernikahan. Pada hari pernikahan, Adif tidak muncul, dan Afeeq mahu membatalkan majlis, membuat Rian sedih.

Mereka berkenalan dengan dua wanita cantik, Syafa (Cut Meyriska) dan Dianti (Marsha Aruan), tetapi menghadapi pelbagai rintangan, termasuk kehadiran mantan kekasih Syafa, Diego (Bastian Steel)

programme.desc: Seorang lelaki bersenjata yang tidak dikenali menceroboh kediaman Aguinaldo, menyebabkan dua cedera. Syukurlah, Alex dan Noel hanya luka ringan . Tetapi Faith sangat terkesan secara emosi dan dalam ketakutan.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep20
programme.desc: Untuk menghalang Carl daripada mengejarnya, Hope dan Eric berpura-pura bertunang. Jose dan Faith rasakan tidndakkan berpura-pura ini tidak perlu.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep21
programme.desc: Faith hampir menangkap Jose menanam komputer riba Joy di belakang rumah. Malangnya, Faith menerima rahsianya yang lebih mengejutkan. Hope terjumpa maklumat yang mengejutkan berkaitan tuduhan merogol beberapa tahun lalu ke atas Jose.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep22
programme.desc: Andi tiba untuk tinggal di rumah agam untuk membantu Hope, juga kerana teman lelakinya memukulnya. Panggilan telefon daripada Javier mendorong Faith untuk berjumpa dengan pemberi pinjaman untuk akhirnya menyelesaikan hutang Love.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep23
programme.desc: Hope bersemuka dengan Jose untuk perkara sebenar tentang kes rogolnya, tetapi kebenaran itu lebih buruk daripada apa yang dia jangkakan. Faith terselamat daripada penculikan oleh anak buah Javier.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep24
programme.desc: Semua orang kelihatan terpesona dengan pembantu Hope yang cantik, Mylene mempunyai keraguan tentang Andi. Dan dia betul, kerana Andi memang ada agenda lain dan sama sekali tidak seperti yang difikirkan oleh bosnya.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep25
programme.desc: Andi, berkawan dengan semua orang: dia sediakan makanan, mendengar luahan, murah hati dengan pujian, dan juga menuruti semua orang untuk mengambil hati. Tetapi Hope menyedari kelakuan andi yang pelik dan merasakan andi hanya berpura-pura.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep26
programme.desc: Andi memberitahu Alex bahawa dia tahu Alex sudah berkahwin. Ini menimbulkan kemarahan Alex, dan dia menyelar Joy kerana memberitahu Andi rahsia mereka. Carl, yang sudah muak dan tidak berpuas hati dengan Love, menyediakan surat cerai mereka.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep06
programme.desc: Selesai kenduri kesyukuran di Kelantan, Tn Badrul mempelawa Mek Yan memperluaskan bisnes dan berbual sehingga larut malam. Faizul hanya mengintai sebab tak mahu terlepas lagi malam "bersama" Shira. Faizul dan Shira pulang ke KL menyambung sesi pengajian. Selepas hantar Shira ke kolej, Faizul berniaga burger. Suatu hari, Shira tergugat dengan kehadiran Sha. Faizul perkenalkan Shira isterinya. Wajah Sha berubah dan hampa. Sha mula menyimpan dendam dan merancang sesuatu untuk dapatkan semula Faizul. programme.desc: Rian tidak yakin dengan Adif, terutamanya kerana Adif sering mengusiknya sebagai anak orang kaya yang mengada, sombong, penting diri sendiri. Rian terkejut apabila rombongan merisik Adif tiba tanpa sebarang perbincangan terlebih dahulu. Adif meminta maaf dan berjanji akan lebih terbuka. Namun, cemburu melihat Adif bersama Rian menyebabkan Afeeq menasihati Rian untuk membatalkan pertunangan. Adif mendengar melalui talian telefon yang belum di off kan oleh Rian tanpa sengaja. Adif marah, menambah ketegangan dalam hubungannya dengan Rian dan sakit hati dengan Afeeq.

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind S1 Ep22
programme.desc: Di pejabat, Zahlia sedaya upaya memakai pakaian yang menjolok mata dengan harapan dapat meraih perhatian Aidil malangnya Aidil menegur Zahlia agar memakai pakaian yang lebih sopan. Zahlia semakin marah dengan sikap Aidil. Ain mengajak Aidil untuk menjemput Muaz di lapangan terbang dan dia beritahu suaminya yang dia sudah memindahkan semua barang-barangnya ke bilik utama kerana takut Muaz akan menyangka yang bukan-bukan. Muaz terus masuk ke pejabat pada hari berikutnya. Zahlia amat terkejut dan marah apabila ditukarkan menjadi PA Adila dan bukannya Aidil. Nak dijadikan cerita, Aidil dan Adila kena berjumpa dengan pelabur projek mereka di Sarawak. Oleh itu PA mereka harus ikut sekali. Zahlia sudah memasang strategi malangnya terkejut apabila mendapati Aidil akan membawa isterinya ke sana. Begitu banyak soalan yang Zahlia tanya sampai Muaz jadi pelik kenapa Zahlia begitu sibuk dengan Aidil.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep13
programme.desc: Yasmin menggunakan Erina untuk mendapatkan semula Syarikat YAS dari datuknya, namun ditolak datuknya menolak. Tibatiba muncul Amar yang baru kembali dari Amerika tanpa memberitahu terlebih dahulu. Amar telah sembuh sepenuhnya dari sakit saraf. Rusdi memberitahu kepada Yasmin dia telah berkahwin dengan Sherry sebagai isteri kedua. Yasmin tidak dapat menerimanya, berlaku pertengkaran dengan suaminya, Rusdi mahu membalas dendam dengan kelakuan Yasmin yang terlalu pentingkan diri sendiri. Yasmin mengalami tekanan perasaan sehingga membuat dirinya separuh gila. Sofia masih belum mengetahui kisah sebenarnya Amar, Iqbal meminta pemuda tersebut bertemu dengan Sofia dan memaklumkan keadaan sebenar dirinya. Amar mengetahui dari bapanya bahawa dia sudah mempunyai anak hasil perkahwinan dengan Sofia bernama Khalif. Amar ingin kembali dengan Sofia, namun Sofia menolak dan meminta Erina mengahwini Amar semula, dia sanggup menjadi rakan baik mereka. Yasmin pula terpaksa mendapatkan rawatan kerana telah hilang waras akibat tekanan perasaan

programme.desc: Ikuti Suffren dan Banni dalam jelajah mereka menikmati makanan-makanan terbaik dari gerai, warung dan kedai kaki lima. Untuk episod kali ini, mereka akan pergi ke Wakey Breaky, Dhon Burger, Kiosk Dessert dan The Mee Syndicate Cafe.

programme.title: Destinasi Bajet S5 Ep07
programme.desc: Dengan bajet yang minimum untuk penginapan, makan minum dan cenderahati untuk tiga hari dua malam ikuti pengembaraan cara destinasi bajet. Bersama Zetty Nabila, ikuti pemgembaraan ke Bandar Diraja Klang.

programme.title: Pengantin Malam
programme.desc: Razif, suami Maya cuba untuk tidak membiarkan cerita hidup lama dibelenggu isteri tercinta dan tidak mahu membiarkan Maya rasa bersalah kerana melanggar Laila. Razif akhirnya membawa Maya ke vila untuk bertenang buat seketika. Dalam masa yang sama, Razif mahu Maya tidak cuba untuk menarik balik kes pelanggaran yang menyebabkan kematian Suzana. Dalam perjalanan ke vila Razif memilih destinasi, Maya terasa seperti pernah menggunakan jalan itu dan dia berasa seperti perkara buruk telah berlaku di kawasan itu, tetapi masih tidak boleh ingat.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Hariz mulai punyai suspek baru iaitu Budi yang sebelum ini hanya baik dan dilihat sebagai peminat setianya. Namun Hariz dapat tahu di rumah Budi ada seorang lelaki tua diikat kaki tangannya. Siapa lelaki ini?

programme.title: Karantina
programme.desc: 5 pelajar pergi ke lawatan sekolah di Pulau Karantina untuk kelas Sejarah. Tetapi salah seorang daripada mereka akan tersesat ke hospital terbiar dan rakan sekelasnya perlu mencarinya, menghadapi ancaman paranormal di sepanjang jalan.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong 2
programme.desc: Kham enggan menjual gajahnya Khon kepada peniaga, Suchart Vilawandei yang bercadang untuk menjualnya kepada seseorang yang bekerja untuk gangster LC. Kham kemudiannya mendapati Vilawandei mati di rumahnya di Bangkok, dan dua anak saudaranya, ahli silat Ping-ping dan Sue-sue, menganggap dia bertanggungjawab. Semasa melarikan diri dari mereka, Kham bertemu rakan lamanya Sarjan Mark, yang memberitahu Kham tentang rancangan pengganas untuk mengganggu rundingan damai Kantana di Bangkok.

programme.title: Budak Pendamping
programme.desc: Ia mengisahkan tentang seorang budak yang berumur 16 tahun, bernama Firash. Dibesarkan sebagai seorang anak tunggal di sebuah keluarga yang sentiasa sibuk dengan kerjaya, membuatkan Firash lebih senang bersendiriaan. Disebabkan itu keluarganya membuat keputusan untuk hantarnya ke sebuah kem. Disana Firash bertembung dengan Idlan dan rakannya Khai dan Sahar, serta sebahagian dalam Ahli Majlis Tertinggi Asrama (AMTA) bagi kem tersebut. Akibat ketidakpuasan mereka terhadap Firash yang kelihatan lembik, badannya menjadi tempat untuk mereka lepaskan kekerasan. Namun kehadiran budak pendamping mengubah segalanya untuk Firash tetapi ia juga menggugat kesejahteraan yang dah lama tidak bergelora. Lantas, adakah perjanjian antara Firash dan pendampingnya merupakan ilusi semata - mata ataupun terdapat hutang yang akan dituntut antaranya dengan Tuan Daud?

programme.title: Plan B Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke-2 mengisahkan Khai berjaya memujuk Airis menemankannya minum setelah membawanya bersiar-siar melihat suasana Kuala Lumpur dari udara dengan kapal terbang jenis ringan miliknya. Que pula seorang pelajar kolej salah seorang daripada rakan Khai sedang diintip dan diekori polis. Kemudian Airis bersetuju berlumba kereta secara haram dengan Khai, sebagai satu syarat untuk keluar bagi kali kedua bersama-sama minum dengannya. Setelah Khai memenangi perlumbaan kereta iru, Airis seterusnya mencabar Khai supaya melakukan aktiviti yang lebih mencabar, iaitu mencuri kereta, kononnya sematamata sebagai satu hiburan sahaja.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Hariz mulai punyai suspek baru iaitu Budi yang sebelum ini hanya baik dan dilihat sebagai peminat setianya. Namun Hariz dapat tahu di rumah Budi ada seorang lelaki tua diikat kaki tangannya. Siapa lelaki ini?

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Detektif Khairul Malik menyimpan sebuah rahsia, yang teman wanitanya, Aisya tidak tahu mengenainya. Perkara menjadi rumit dengan penemuan mayat dua puluh tahun, yang menggerakkan rangkaian kejadian yang membawa maut. Kehidupannya berubah secara mendadak apabila dia bertemu Sofia, gadis yang berkebolehan meramal kematian orang. Apabila dia meramal sebuah tragedi dahsyat, Sofia mendapat perhatian polis dan juga seorang keturunan usahawan insurans ulung, Lokman Nazir. Tertarik dengan bakat unik Sofia, Malik meyakinkan dia untuk bekerja bersamanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa, tetapi niat baik mereka menyebabkan tragedi. Sementara itu, penghantaran sebuah pita menyebabkan huru-hara dalam hubungan Malik dan Aisya apabila rahsia gelap Aisya mula terungkai.

programme.title: Hantu Bungkus Ikat Tepi
programme.desc: Cerita ini mengisahkan tentang 3 rakan baik, FUAD, FADLI dan FENDI yang masing-masing mempunyai pekerjaan sederhana dan cukup-cukup makan. Mereka nampak berani namun sebenarnya penakut. Cerita bermula apabila mereka menaiki kereta di satu malam, tiba-tiba terlihat seorang lelaki terbaring di atas jalan dengan berlumuran darah di badan. Fuad, Fadli dan Fendi rasa tak senang duduk kerana pisau yang berada di sebelah mayat itu dipegang dan membuat mereka rasa bersalah dan dicop pembunuh, lalu memutuskan untuk menanam mayat tersebut di satu kawasan.

programme.title: Binhi

Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

Desta membesar menjadi seorang yang menyendiri dan penuh misteri. Keinginannya untuk membalas dendam membuatkan dia mencari dalang di sebalik kematian ibu bapanya.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Di pinggir Jawa, Indonesia, pengembara dari dekat dan jauh meninjau sesuatu yang aneh dan misteri. sebuah keluarga yang mencari tempat tinggal selepas pengebumian nenek mereka dan pasangan muda bercinta mencari tempat untuk bermalam bersama. Walau bagaimanapun, perkara-perkara tidak seperti yang mereka nampak di losmen

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Seorang bapa yang ingin membalas dendam atas kematian isteri dan anaknya yang terbunuh mengikuti pembunuh, seorang pengutip hutang, kepada losmen pada suatu malam. Dengan pembunuh yang tinggal di bilik sebelah, kali ini hantu berlaku bukan dalam satu bilik tetapi dua. Dalam kejutan yang mengejutkan, di antara harta benda si mati, Golok menjumpai keratan akhbar lama yang menggambarkan sebuah keluarga yang hilang di motel berhantu itu, membayangkan bahawa bukan kebetulan mereka terjumpa Losmen Melati pada malam sebelumnya. Berapa ramai lagi yang tahu tentang rumah tamu terkutuk itu dan apakah masalah masa depan yang akan dibawa oleh ini?

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 3 Ep3
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah suasana yang tidak menentu, Melati dan Golok dikejutkan dengan kedatangan tetamu luar biasa, Wewe Gombel, yang telah menghidu mangsanya di halaman Melati Inn. Ketika Melati dan Golok cuba mengejar dan menundukkannya, rahsia silam Melati terbongkar, akhirnya membawa Wewe Gombel untuk mencari apa yang dia cari.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Apabila salah seorang pemandu trak tunda muncul mati dan seorang lagi masih hilang, Detektif Fadil dari balai polis tempatan mula membuat hubungan antara kes terbarunya dan Losmen Melati. Dia mula bertanya soalan dan menghantar orang barunya, Osman, menyamar untuk mengetahui apa yang sebenarnya berlaku di losmen misteri itu. Tetapi apabila Osman hilang, Fadil bergegas ke losmen untuk mencarinya, hanya untuk melencong apabila dia melihat sesosok bayangan gelap di jalan raya di hadapannya, menyebabkan dia terbabas. Fadil sedar ada sesuatu yang lebih besar sedang bermain.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Adnan, seorang penunggang motosikal jalanan yang yatim piatu dan dijaga oleh bibinya. Di pihak lain, Nadia dilahirkan dalam keluarga yang kaya dan kini memiliki pekerjaan yang stabil. Kedua-dua individu yang berlatarbelakangkan dunia yang berbeza ini akhirnya bertemu secara kebetulan dan terjalin hubungan antara mereka.

programme.desc: Samad bekerja sebagai pelukis komik di sebuah syarikat. Dia selalu sibuk dengan kerjanya sehingga sering mengabaikan keluarga dan tunangnya. Pada suatu malam, Samad terlibat dalam satu kemalangan jalan raya. Apabila tersedar daripada pengsan, Samad bertemu dengan Adika, watak hero dalam komik yang dicipta olehnya. Samad menyedari bahawa dia secara tidak sengaja telah termasuk ke dalam dunia komik ciptaannya itu. Dalam masa yang sama, Adika meminta bantuan daripada Samad untuk menghadapi ancaman daripada Jalak, watak penjahat dalam komik itu. Berjayakah Samad membantu Adika dan seterusnya mencari jalan keluar untuk kembali ke dunia nyata?

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the Hand of God?

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong 2012
programme.desc: Soon-to-be-retired weather presenter Kwok Ching has always dream of becoming a news anchor. Being a single parent, he interferes in every aspect of his childrens lives, causing them to move away from him. When Kwok Ching receives a doomsday news and finally has the chance to become a news anchor, it is also time to reunite with his family.

programme.title: Nezha
programme.desc: A former top team racing driver wants to prove himself in a race but accidentally hurts his teammate Lily, leading to the teams downfall. When an inexperienced virtual car racing champion joins the team and unexpectedly shines in a real-life race, can the three drivers team up to regain glory for their team?

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
programme.desc: Starring four Hong Kong Film Awards Best Actors, Simon Yam, Louis Koo, Tony Leung Ka Fai and Gordon Lam, this action-thriller follows the real-life kidnapping events that terrorized Hong Kongs elite in the 1990s by serial billionaire-kidnapper Logan and his gang.

programme.title: The Exodus
programme.desc: A low-ranking cop discovers a group of women, including his superior, Madam Fong and his wife, plotting to eliminate the world of men.

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Saving General Yang
programme.desc: The Khitan army takes revenge for a past massacre by abducting General Yang Ye and setting up a deadly trap for the seven Yang brothers. Led by the eldest son, the seven brothers set out with a small band of fighters to bring their father home.

programme.title: You are the One
programme.desc: A talented rogue trader experiences a 180-degree change in life when he encounters a girl who does not believe good things will happen to her. Will they fall in love? It seems like a Cinderellas adventure has just begun!

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Wise Guys Never Die
programme.desc: Nick meets Teddy, a con artiste, when he is sent to prison for embezzlement, and Teddy teaches him all the gambling tricks. After their release, they team up with Teddys lover Lora, to take revenge on Dragon, who framed Teddy for his sentence. Nick though is seduced by Lora and they end up in an affair. Will Nick finally join Teddy in his revenge?

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Rus financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the clients data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the faade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Old Fox
programme.desc: In 1989, young Liao Jie and his father save for a home, unaware of rising property prices. Frustrated by poverty, he learns from their landlord Old Fox who teaches him survival in society. Liao Jie ends up hurting Old Fox with what he has learnt, but his empathy prevents him from becoming like Old Fox.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: The White Storm 3 Heaven or Hell
programme.desc: Hong Kong cop Billy works undercover in Suchat's drug cartel, while another undercover cop Wing successfully earns their trust in an incident and a brotherly bond is built among the three. When the police busts the syndicate, Suchat flees to the Golden Triangle with Billy and receives a tip-off about the betrayal within his circle of trust

programme.title: Old Fox
programme.desc: In 1989, young Liao Jie and his father save for a home, unaware of rising property prices. Frustrated by poverty, he learns from their landlord Old Fox who teaches him survival in society. Liao Jie ends up hurting Old Fox with what he has learnt, but his empathy prevents him from becoming like Old Fox.

programme.title: Ashes of Time Redux
programme.desc: After his beloved woman married his brother, Ou Yang Feng moves to the desert to run an inn and becomes a killer agent. He makes acquaintance of different people with their different stories ... The movie is the winner of the 1st Hong Kong Film Critics Society Awards for Best Film, Best Director, Best Screenplay and Best Actor (Leslie Cheung).

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe (Jaycee Chan) is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora (Fiona Sit). After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong (the director, playing herself). Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend (Patrick Tang) and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist (Hayama Hiro) threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: S Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk witnesses a suspects murder while investigating an illegal soccer gambling case, but is unable to disclose information to Chief Inspector Lau due to his code of confidentiality, thereby hindering Laus investigation. While starting the case with mutual distrust, they end up reaching a rapport to uproot the crime syndicate.

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chefs delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: The Enchanting Ghost
programme.desc: It is love beyond the grave, as a young scholar and his beautiful lover are torn apart forever by his dastardly uncle and his friend, who drive the girl to commit suicide... but with death comes revenge for the enchanting ghost. A spooky yet heart-wrenching tale...

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charns beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dongs concubine as he knows Dongs adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: Buddha's Palm
programme.desc: Young Long Jian Fei, a martial arts novice, is adopted by the Fire Spirit Demon who taught him the powerful Buddha's Palm, turning Long into a martial arts master. Long is tasked by the Fire Spirit Demon to takes revenge for his master, and this soon unleashes a storm upon the martial arts world

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: Lady Of Steel
programme.desc: A young swordswoman Fang Ying Qi sets out to join the Flying Dragon Clan in their defense against the invading Jin forces. Fang also intends to avenge the murder of her parents by bandit leader Han 20 years ago. Han has since taken on a false identity as a member of the Flying Dragon Clan and Fang must rely on her deadly sword skills to stop Han.

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: The Shadow Whip
programme.desc: Three hundred thousand worth of silver is robbed by a thief using a whip as the weapon. As it is a signature weapon used by a martial arts master Shadow Whip, he is suspected and hunted. No one sees him after that. Fifteen years later, a young girl Yang shows up using the same weapon. Who is this girl and what has happened to Shadow Whip?

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Village of Tigers
programme.desc: The devilish residents of the Village of Tigers, led by Hu Jiao, plan to kill Lo Hong Shun, otherwise known as the heroic Sword of the Southern Sky. Hu Jiao sees a way to use the righteousness of the honorable Ba family to help him kill the hero Lo by turning them against him. Will good prevail over evil?

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperors sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: Threatened by the Yuan who are closing in to rule the whole of China, a band of Song survivors band together to save their prime minister. This bold and fearless heroes fighting for their cause are led by international star, Lo Lieh (Glass Tears, Killer Clans) and Shi Szu (Lovers Destiny), who must fight their way out of trap after trap. But they can't escape them all, and eventually the two end up in prison... it is either death or a fight to the end!

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Return of Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A band of ninjas slaughters the entire Wu Dang Clan and frames Du Gu Wu Di, chief of the Invincible Clan, for the deed. Yun masters the silkworm martial arts style and decides to take revenge for the Clan by challenging Wu Di, but is defeated and seriously hurt. Luckily, Master Li saves and treats him, allowing Yun to avoid the ninjas pursuit.

programme.title: The Kingdom and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chans first major movies) for an evocative and terrific Martial arts world adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: The Assassin
programme.desc: Notorious assassin Nieh Cheng has retired into hiding. However, when Premier Yen's family is massacred, he seeks out the reclusive swordsman and coaxes him into a final revenge mission in this epic story set in the Six Kingdom era.

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Lis new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress. Empress Liu is convicted for her act and Consort Li finally reunites with her son who is now the Emperor.

programme.title: Little Hero
programme.desc: An orphan, Little Bastard is taken on and trained as a fighter by a hermit. When Little Bastard grows up, he feels he is old enough to go out and look for his parents. Luckily for him, he befriends a beggar, Hsiao Yi, who being street-wise, manages to help him find his family, but somehow gets into trouble with the gang.

programme.title: The Twin Bracelets
programme.desc: Two teenage girls make a pledge to look after each other in a small Chinese fishing town, where the notions of women's rights or sexual freedom are absent. One ends up happily married to a stranger, while the other is cruelly betrothed to the abusive son of a wealthy family and has to seek to free herself from the situation.

programme.title: Duel For Gold
programme.desc: Six swordsmen, including two sisters and their husbands, a ranger and a security man, are trying to steal a million gold taels from the Fu Lai Treasury House, not knowing that one of them is actually an undercover hero. In their quest, they have to double-cross and outwit one another...

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: Magnificent Wanderers
programme.desc: Lin and his two friends are traveling patriots who vow to stand up against violence and fight for justice. They meet a rich young man Chu by chance one day and the four become best friends. When a foreign prince plots to possess Chus family fortune and goes after him, Lin and friends go all out to help Chu fight against the villain.

programme.title: The Crimson Charm
programme.desc: In attempting to rescue some innocent people, swordsman Chiang Tzu-chao (Fang Mien) slays the son of Tsao Kang (Wang Hsia), leader of the ruthless Crimson Charm gang.The enraged father promises vengeance on the day of Chiang's 60th birthday...

programme.title: The Magic Blade
programme.desc: The movie depicts Fu Hong Xue fighting against the formidable conspirator Master Yu and seeing through his deception. The brilliantly choreographed fights, glorious settings, superb cinematography and strong casts define this movie as a highpoint in Wu Xia cinema.

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: The Swordmates
programme.desc: Li asks his swordmate Wang to protect his family while he is away, but Wang rapes his wife and even has his convoy attacked. Li escaped but fears his daughter is still in danger, so he asks the nephew of his master to help protect her

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Long Road to Gallantry
programme.desc: Tu Meng Fei makes his way to the world after completing his kung fu training. En route, he rescues Mu Wan Erh and Li San Nan from a band of thugs and later learnt of a 20-year conflict between the evil Thunder Gang Chief Leng Tian Lei and the Dragon Sect. Mus lost father is none other than the Thunder Gang Chief, who also killed Lis father

programme.desc: Get to know Fera, the Queen of the Pantanal, as she teaches her rambunctious cub Simba how to climb trees and hunt for dinner. Then learn why Ferinha, another local female, struggles with motherhood as more males move in and threaten the youngsters.

programme.title: Jaguar Journals 1 - Collar Complications Ep3

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 1 - Movin’ on Up Ep2

programme.title: Rooted 1 - Sweet Seduction Ep2
programme.desc: Discover the story of the much loved Sausage Tree, whose nectar filled blooms and sausage shaped fruits entice animals of all kinds, from insects to elephants. See how the very animals who rely on this generous tree ensure its proliferation.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Socorro Islands Ep2
programme.desc: A tiny volcanic archipelago rising from the untamed waters of the eastern Pacific, the Socorro Islands have been called the Mexican Galapagos. Get ready for jaw-dropping encounters with giant Pacific manta rays, dolphins, and white tip reef sharks.

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Bahamas Ep3

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 1 - Belize Ep4
programme.desc: More than 200 caves play host to an unmatched array of marine life and coral formations in this underwater kingdom 40 kilometres from Belize City. It's a deep blue wilderness brimming with rare, exotic fish, eagle rays, sharks, and huge green morays.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - The Garden Route Ep1

Fire and wind fuel growth in great diversity and rock shapes a coastline of many faces. Life thrives here - from the magnificent to the bizarre. This is the Garden Route National Park.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - Kruger's Pafuri Ep2
programme.desc: In the northern reaches of the Kruger National Park, life depends on one thing water. In a land burdened by heat and drought a single ribbon cuts its reliable course through the wilderness. Its a lifeline to all creatures, great and small.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 2 - Augrabies Falls Ep3
programme.desc: Augrabies is where the mighty Orange River plunges over the awesome 56 meter Augrabies waterfall. Derived from a word oukurubes which means place of thunder in the indigenous language of the Nama-Khoi this land is the heart of a harsh and sun-beaten world with flashes of brilliant color and a thunderous roar.

programme.title: Malawi Wildlife Rescue 1 - The Great Escape Ep3

programme.title: Malawi Wildlife Rescue 1 - Big Buck Chase Ep4

programme.title: Malawi Wildlife Rescue 1 - Creatures Great and Small Ep5

programme.title: Malawi Wildlife Rescue 1 - Catch Me if You Can Ep6
